From 922eeca5e02423187348b395f1a7b5a15d8f1e85 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mayank Singh <mayankfz@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Apr 2026 06:02:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] add support for Azure Container Linux

- Create standalone AclOSUtil(DefaultOSUtil) in acl.py so that future
  Azure-Linux changes do not inadvertently affect the immutable ACL image.
- Override get_systemd_unit_file_install_path() to /etc/systemd/system
  to fix read-only filesystem error on sysext overlay.
- Add retry logic in mount_resource_disk() for VMBus storage race.
- Add ACL-specific waagent.conf, waagent.service, and sysext drop-in.
- Document the sysext drop-in (10-waagent-sysext.conf).
- Patch persist_firewall_rules.py service template to add After=systemd-sysext.service
  so the dynamically-created waagent-network-setup.service waits for sysext merge.
- Add ACL owner entry in CODEOWNERS.
